verbose_text: Additionally, we found that decreases in the levels of ScFvEGFR specific IgG or IgM producing B cells in the mice that received the targeted IONP-Dox were not due to non specific immune suppression effects or cytotoxic effect of Dox on B lymphocytes since ELISPOT assay revealed that the total numbers of IgG producing B cells were not decreased in the spleen.
evidence: levels of ScFvEGFR specific IgG or IgM
